            eyeNAV stands out as a pioneer in the field, offering specialized
            360째 photography services to numerous hotels and resorts. Our focus
            has been on delivering top-notch 360째 Photography for luxury hotel
            brands across Asia.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="bg-purple rounded-full p-4"></div>
            <div class="border-l border-purple h-full w-0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="max-w-[60ch] p-10 pt-0">
