          </div>
          <div class="max-w-[60ch] p-10 pt-0">
            Recognizing the importance of meticulous planning to ensure optimal
            results without compromising the guest experience, eyeNAV is
            committed to achieving excellence in every project.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="bg-purple rounded-full p-4"></div>
            <div class="border-l border-purple h-full w-0"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="max-w-[60ch] p-10 pt-0">
            For cluster projects within the Asia Pacific region, eyeNAV goes the
            extra mile by absorbing travel costs, demonstrating our dedication
            to delivering comprehensive solutions.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex">
